Data Deletion Request
If you would like to request the deletion of your personal data that we have collected through the Bubble Pop Mania game, please follow the steps below:

Send an email to abhaylathiya26@gmail.com with the subject line "Data Deletion Request".
In the body of the email, please provide the following information:
Your full name
The email address associated with your game account
A clear and specific request for data deletion
We will process your data deletion request within a reasonable timeframe and take necessary steps to delete your personal information from our records, as long as it is within the scope of our legal obligations.

Please note that certain data may be retained for backup purposes or to comply with legal requirements. However, we will ensure that any retained data is protected in accordance with this privacy policy.

For any further questions or concerns regarding your data deletion request or our privacy practices, please feel free to reach out to us using the contact information provided.

